        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Pell Grant Flexibility Act of 201</b><b>7</b></p> <p> This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude from gross income any amount received as a Federal Pell Grant awarded under the Higher Education Act of 1965. </p>]]></text>
